						src="/images/BlazorIcon.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Blazor Logo"></a>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h1 class="card-title">Blazor</h1>
					<p class="card-text">Blazor is a powerful framework for creating rich, interactive web applications
						using C# instead of JavaScript. It simplifies the development process and enhances productivity.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="card m-2 p-2" style="width: 18rem;">
				<a href="https://dotnet.microsoft.com/apps/aspnet" target="_blank"><img src="/images/ASP-NET-logo.png"
						class="card-img-top" alt="Dot Net Logo"></a>
