			</div>
			<div class="card m-2 p-2" style="width: 15rem;">
				<a href="https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/" target="_blank"><img src="/images/VisualStudioLogo.png"
						class="card-img-top" alt="Dot Net Logo"></a>
				<div class="card-body">
					<h1 class="card-title">Visual Studio</h1>
					<p class="card-text">Visual Studio is renowned for its comprehensive suite of tools that support a
						wide range of programming languages and development tasks, making it a powerful IDE for
						developers.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

